"About us:
INSIEME was founded in the year 2019 and providing continuous services till the data.INSIEME is registered as non-profit organization.Our INSIEME family consists of more than 69 nationalities.Our main activities include promoting cultural initiatives, bureaucratic documentations, meetings and other activities.

Mission:
Our mission is to facilitate meaningful involvement, community engagement and leadership development, which enable all students to contribute a global society.

Vision:
Our vision is to develop well rounded, confident and responsible individuals who are confident enough to integrate with international community. We will do this by providing a welcoming, happy, safe and supportive environment in which everyone is equal and all achievements are celebrated."
